    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer who values a well-documented history and consistent care. The exterior maintains a deep, reflective luster, free of major blemishes and showing only the minor, honest character marks of a well-loved car. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of cleanliness; the upholstery is supple and free of tears, while every switch, dial, and digital display functions exactly as it did the day it left the showroom. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health, having undergone regular preventative maintenance and fluid services to ensure a smooth, responsive, and quiet ride. From the cold AC to the tight suspension, this car delivers a confident driving experience with no surprises. It is a complete, reliable package ready for its next chapter.",
