      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm parting with my reliable ride, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014super clean inside and out, with just the usual minor love marks you'd expect from a well-loved car. It runs like a dream and is ready for its next adventure with you! Feel free to reach out with any questions; I'd love to see it go to a good home.",
