    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the legendary S54 naturally aspirated 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power with a razor-sharp 8,000 RPM redline. Power is sent to the rear wheels via a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock for optimal corner-exit traction. The chassis remains composed thanks to a refreshed suspension featuring Bilstein dampers and poly-bushes. Crucially, the Vanos system has been professionally overhauled and the rear subframe reinforced\u2014essential preventative maintenance for this platform. While the aesthetics show minor patina consistent with spirited use, the mechanical synchronization and throttle response from the individual throttle bodies remain peerless.",
